### Register a new user
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/users/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Juma",
  "password": "Juma123"
}

### Login to get the authentication token
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Juma",
  "password": "Juma123"
}

### Send a message to the chatbot (replace YOUR_TOKEN with the actual token from login)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat/send_message/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token 9feac493e328d31e379d94f08d386ecdeea525df

{
  "message": "Hello AI!"
}

### Check token balance (replace YOUR_TOKEN with the actual token)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/tokens/balance/
Authorization: Token YOUR_TOKEN
